testsuite.name: Test cases for resource versions in run triggers

testcase.name: WORKFLOW_TESTS - pipeline workFlow tests Test cases for resource versions in run triggers P_WF_7379_001 A user posts 20 resourceVersions of a resource that is a triggering input to a pipeline. All 20 runs are created and each has a different resourceVersionId in the runResourceVersion.
